name: Savalan Lake is known as Sultan and the habitat of bears is brown.
description:
The peak that has a lake in its heart.

The people of the region swear by this mountain and lake.

The lake does not freeze for only 2 months of the year.

Some locals swim in it, while the water temperature is less than 10 degrees.

It takes 40 km to reach this lake at an altitude of 4811 meters above sea level.
